com.ibm.xmi.framework
Class ObjectInfo

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.ibm.xmi.framework.ObjectInfo
public class ObjectInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds information about an object that the framework acquires when it parses an XMI file. You can query an instance of this class to determine what kind of object to make when you implement a reader adapter.
